## bug fix
- To support the follow case: use  box-shadow and  pseudo-class,update box-shadow logic to fix bug
    - demo:http://dotwe.org/vue/bda48e3c453f1eb6f28732c5063f3bbf

-  rax in follow case will re-render , so save flag to recovery
    - demo
```html
import {createElement, Component, render} from 'rax';
import {Text} from 'rax-components';

class App extends Component {
  constructor(props){
  	super(props);
    this.state = {
      test: '1'
    }
  }
  press(){
   this.setState({
    	test: this.state.test === '1' ?'2':'1'
    })
  }
  render() { 
    return (
      <Text style={Styles.item} onPress={this.press.bind(this)}>233{this.state.test}</Text>
    );
  }
}
const Styles = {
	item:{
      	backgroundColor:'red',
        'backgroundColor:active':'blue'
    }
}
render(<App />);

```

